 Query Execution'=>'多查询执行','Persisted Queries'=>'持久化查询','Query Functions'=>'查询函数','Schema Functions'=>'Schema 函数','All Gato GraphQL PRO extensions (including upcoming ones): All the “Power Extensions”, plus all the “Premium Extensions”'=>'所有 Gato GraphQL PRO 扩展（包括即将推出的扩展）：全部“Power Extensions”，外加全部“Premium Extensions”','All of Gato GraphQL\'s power extensions, in a single plugin'=>'所有 Gato GraphQL 的强大扩展，集于一个插件','Define Access Control Lists to manage granular access to the API for your users'=>'定义访问控制列表，以管理用户对 API 的细粒度访问权限','Make your application faster by providing HTTP Caching for the GraphQL response, and by caching the results of expensive operations'=>'通过为 GraphQL 响应提供 HTTP 缓存，以及缓存高消耗操作的结果，让您的应用程序运行更快','Create custom schemas, with custom access rules for different users, each available under its own endpoint'=>'创建自定义模式，为不同用户设置自定义访问规则，每个规则在其自己的端点下可用','Evolve the GraphQL schema by deprecating fields, and explaining how to replace them, through a user interface'=>'通过用户界面弃用字段并说明如何替换它们，从而演进 GraphQL 模式','Connect to and interact with external services via their APIs'=>'通过其 API 连接并与外部服务进行交互','Execute GraphQL queries directly within your application, using PHP code'=>'使用 PHP 代码在您的应用程序中直接执行 GraphQL 查询','Combine multiple GraphQL queries together, and execute them as a single operation, to improve performance and make your queries more manageable'=>'将多个 GraphQL 查询合并在一起，并作为单个操作执行，以提高性能并使查询更易于管理','Use GraphQL queries to create pre-defined endpoints as in REST, obtaining the benefits from both APIs'=>'使用 GraphQL 查询创建类似 REST 的预定义端点，同时获得两种 API 的优势','Manipulate the values of fields within the GraphQL query, via a collection of utilities and special directives providing meta-programming capabilities'=>'通过一系列实用工具和提供元编程能力的特殊指令，操纵 GraphQL 查询中字段的值','Collection of fields and directives added to the GraphQL schema, providing useful functionality'=>'添加到 GraphQL 模式中的字段和指令集合，提供实用功能','Access Control: Visitor IP'=>'访问控制：访客 IP','Cache Control'=>'缓存控制','Conditional Field Manipulation'=>'条件字段操控','Deprecation Notifier'=>'废弃通知器','Email Sender'=>'邮件发送器','Field Default Value'=>'字段默认值','Field Deprecation'=>'字段废弃','Field on Field'=>'字段作用于字段','Field Resolution Caching'=>'字段解析缓存','Field Response Removal'=>'字段响应移除','Field To Input'=>'字段转输入','Field Value Iteration and Manipulation'=>'字段值迭代与操控','Helper Function Collection'=>'辅助函数集合','HTTP Request via Schema'=>'通过模式发起 HTTP 请求','Low-Level Persisted Query Editing'=>'低级持久化查询编辑','PHP Constants and Environment Variables via Schema'=>'通过模式访问 PHP 常量和环境变量','PHP Functions via Schema'=>'通过模式调用 PHP 函数','Response Error Trigger'=>'响应错误触发器','Schema Editing Access'=>'模式编辑访问','Grant granular access to the schema, based on the user being logged-in (or not), having a certain role or capability, and more.'=>'根据用户是否已登录、是否具有特定角色或权限等条件，对模式进行精细化访问控制。','Grant access to the schema based on the visitor\'s IP address (Access Control extension is required).'=>'根据访客 IP 地址授予对模式的访问权限（需要安装访问控制扩展）。','Provide HTTP Caching for endpoints accessed via GET, with the max-age value automatically calculated from the query.'=>'为通过 GET 方式访问的端点提供 HTTP 缓存，max-age 值由查询自动计算得出。','Apply a directive on a field only if some condition is met.'=>'仅在满足某个条件时，将指令应用于字段。','Provide multiple GraphQL endpoints to target different users and applications.'=>'提供多个 GraphQL 端点，以针对不同用户和应用程序。','Send deprecations in the response to the query (and not only when doing introspection).'=>'在查询响应中发送废弃通知（而不仅限于内省时）。','Send emails via global mutation <code>_sendEmail</code>.'=>'通过全局变更 <code>_sendEmail</code> 发送邮件。','Set a field to some default value (whenever it is <code>null</code> or empty).'=>'为字段设置默认值（当其为 <code>null</code> 或空值时）。','Deprecate fields, and explain how to replace them, through a user interface.'=>'通过用户界面废弃字段，并说明如何替换它们。','Manipulate the value of a field by applying some other field on it.'=>'通过将另一个字段应用于某字段来操控其值。','Cache and retrieve the response for expensive field operations.'=>'缓存并检索高开销字段操作的响应。','Remove the output of a field from the response.'=>'从响应中移除字段的输出。','Retrieve the value of a field, manipulate it, and input it into another field, all within the same query.'=>'在同一查询中，获取某字段的值、对其进行操控，并将其输入到另一个字段中。','Iterate and manipulate the value elements of array and object fields.'=>'迭代并操控数组和对象字段的值元素。','Collection of fields providing useful functionality.'=>'提供实用功能的字段集合。','Addition of fields to execute HTTP requests against a webserver and fetch their response.'=>'添加字段以向 Web 服务器执行 HTTP 请求并获取其响应。','Addition of fields to retrieve the current HTTP request data.'=>'添加字段以获取当前 HTTP 请求数据。','Execute GraphQL queries directly within your application, using PHP code.'=>'使用 PHP 代码直接在应用程序中执行 GraphQL 查询。','Make normally-hidden directives (which inject some functionality into the GraphQL server) visible when editing a persisted query.'=>'在编辑持久化查询时，使通常隐藏的指令（用于向 GraphQL 服务器注入某些功能）可见。','Combine multiple queries into a single query, sharing state across them and executing them in the requested order.'=>'将多个查询合并为单个查询，在它们之间共享状态并按请求的顺序执行。','Use GraphQL queries to create pre-defined endpoints as in REST, obtaining the benefits from both APIs.'=>'使用 GraphQL 查询创建类似 REST 的预定义端点，同时获得两种 API 的优势。','Query the value from an environment variable or PHP constant.'=>'从环境变量或 PHP 常量中查询值。','Manipulate the field output using standard programming language functions available in PHP.'=>'使用 PHP 中可用的标准编程语言函数操控字段输出。','Explicitly add an error entry to the response to trigger the failure of the GraphQL request (whenever a field does not meet the expected conditions).'=>'在响应中显式添加错误条目，以便在字段不满足预期条件时触发 GraphQL 请求失败。','Grant access to users other than admins to edit the GraphQL schema.'=>'授权管理员以外的用户编辑 GraphQL 架构。','Automation'=>'自动化','Bricks'=>'Bricks','Elementor'=>'Elementor','Events Manager'=>'Events Manager','JetEngine'=>'JetEngine','MultilingualPress'=>'MultilingualPress','Polylang'=>'Polylang','Translation'=>'翻译','WooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','Use GraphQL to automate tasks in your app: Execute queries when some event happens, chain queries, and schedule and trigger queries via WP-Cron. (The Internal GraphQL Server extension is required).'=>'使用 GraphQL 自动化应用程序中的任务：在某些事件发生时执行查询、链接查询，以及通过 WP-Cron 调度和触发查询。（需要 Internal GraphQL Server 扩展）。','Integration with plugin "Bricks", adding fields to parse and update data in Bricks pages and templates.'=>'与插件 "Bricks" 集成，添加用于解析和更新 Bricks 页面及模板中数据的字段。','Integration with plugin "Elementor", adding fields to parse and update data in Elementor pages and templates.'=>'与插件 "Elementor" 集成，添加用于解析和更新 Elementor 页面及模板中数据的字段。','Integration with plugin "Events Manager", adding fields to the schema to fetch event data.'=>'与插件 "Events Manager" 集成，向架构添加用于获取活动数据的字段。','Integration with plugin "JetEngine", adding fields to the schema to fetch Custom Content Type data.'=>'与插件 "JetEngine" 集成，向架构添加用于获取自定义内容类型数据的字段。','Integration with plugin "MultilingualPress", adding fields to the schema to fetch multilingual data.'=>'与插件 "MultilingualPress" 集成，向架构添加用于获取多语言数据的字段。','Integration with plugin "Polylang", adding fields to the schema to fetch multilingual data.'=>'与插件 "Polylang" 集成，向架构添加用于获取多语言数据的字段。','Translate content to multiple languages using the service provider of your choice, among ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, DeepSeek, Mistral AI, OpenRouter, self-hosted LLM (eg: via Ollama), DeepL, and Google Translate.'=>'使用您选择的服务提供商（包括 ChatGPT、Claude、Gemini、DeepSeek、Mistral AI、OpenRouter、自托管 LLM（如：通过 Ollama）、DeepL 和 Google Translate）将内容翻译成多种语言。','Integration with WooCommerce, to fetch product data.'=>'与 WooCommerce 集成，用于获取产品数据。','ChatGPT Translation'=>'ChatGPT 翻译','Claude Translation'=>'Claude 翻译','DeepL'=>'DeepL','DeepSeek'=>'DeepSeek','Gemini Translation'=>'Gemini 翻译','Google Translate'=>'Google 翻译','JetEngine CCTs'=>'JetEngine CCTs','Mistral AI Translation'=>'Mistral AI 翻译','OpenRouter Translation'=>'OpenRouter 翻译','Self-Hosted LLM Translation'=>'自托管 LLM 翻译','Translate content to multiple languages using the ChatGPT API.'=>'使用 ChatGPT API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using the Claude API.'=>'使用 Claude API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using the DeepL API.'=>'使用 DeepL API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using the DeepSeek API.'=>'使用 DeepSeek API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using the Gemini API.'=>'使用 Gemini API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using the Google Translate API.'=>'使用 Google Translate API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using the Mistral AI API.'=>'使用 Mistral AI API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using the OpenRouter API.'=>'使用 OpenRouter API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using a Self-Hosted LLM provider.'=>'使用自托管 LLM 提供商将内容翻译为多种语言。','Translate content to multiple languages using any provider\'s API.'=>'使用任意提供商的 API 将内容翻译为多种语言。','Oops, the documentation for this module is not available'=>'抱歉，此模块的文档暂不可用','Meta'=>'元数据','Custom Post Meta'=>'自定义文章元数据','User Meta'=>'用户元数据','Comment Meta'=>'评论元数据','Taxonomy Meta'=>'分类元数据','Query meta values'=>'查询元数据值','Query meta values from custom posts (such as type <code>%1$s</code>)'=>'从自定义文章查询元数据值（例如类型 <code>%1$s</code>）','Query meta values from users (for type <code>%1$s</code>)'=>'从用户查询元数据值（适用于类型 <code>%1$s</code>）','Query meta values from comments (for type <code>%1$s</code>)'=>'从评论查询元数据值（适用于类型 <code>%1$s</code>）','Query meta values for taxonomies (such as types <code>%1$s</code> and <code>%2$s</code>)'=>'查询分类法的元数据值（例如类型 <code>%1$s</code> 和 <code>%2$s</code>）','Meta keys'=>'元数据键','List of all the meta keys, to either allow or deny access to, when querying fields <code>metaValue</code> and <code>metaValues</code> on %s (one entry per line).'=>'在 %s 上查询字段 <code>metaValue</code> 和 <code>metaValues</code> 时，允许或拒绝访问的所有元数据键列表（每行一条）。','<strong>Heads up:</strong> Entries surrounded with <code>/</code> or <code>#</code> are evaluated as regex (regular expressions).'=>'<strong>注意：</strong> 以 <code>/</code> 或 <code>#</code> 包围的条目将作为正则表达式（regex）进行解析。','<strong>Example:</strong> Any of these entries match meta key <code>"%1$s"</code>: %2$s'=>'<strong>示例：</strong> 以下任意条目均可匹配元数据键 <code>"%1$s"</code>：%2$s','Treat %s as “sensitive” data'=>'将 %s 视为“敏感”数据','If checked, the <strong>%s</strong> data is exposed in the schema only if the Schema Configuration has option <code>Expose Sensitive Data in the Schema</code> enabled'=>'若勾选，仅当 Schema 配置启用了 <code>Expose Sensitive Data in the Schema</code> 选项时，<strong>%s</strong> 数据才会在 schema 中公开','%1$s<hr/>%2$s<hr/>%3$s%4$s'=>'%1$s<hr/>%2$s<hr/>%3$s%4$s','%s (interface)'=>'%s（接口）','user'=>'用户','comment'=>'评论','taxonomy'=>'分类法','Behavior'=>'行为','Are the entries being allowed or denied access to?'=>'这些条目是被允许还是拒绝访问？','<ul><li>Allow access: only the configured entries can be accessed, and no other can.</li><li>Deny access: the configured entries cannot be accessed, all other entries can.</li></ul>'=>'<ul><li>允许访问：仅允许访问已配置的条目，其他条目均不可访问。</li><li>拒绝访问：已配置的条目不可访问，其他所有条目均可访问。</li></ul>','Allow access'=>'允许访问','Deny access'=>'拒绝访问','%s meta keys'=>'%s 元数据键','User State Mutations'=>'用户状态变更','Meta Mutations'=>'元数据变更','User Meta Mutations'=>'用户元数据变更','Custom Post Mutations'=>'自定义文章变更','Custom Post Meta Mutations'=>'自定义文章元数据变更','Page Mutations'=>'页面变更','Post Mutations'=>'文章变更','Post Meta Mutations'=>'文章元数据变更','Page Meta Mutations'=>'页面元数据变更','Media Mutations'=>'媒体变更','Menu Mutations'=>'菜单变更','Custom Post Media Mutations'=>'自定义文章媒体变更','Page Media Mutations'=>'页面媒体变更','Post Media Mutations'=>'文章媒体变更','Custom Post User Mutations'=>'自定义文章用户变更','Tag Mutations'=>'标签变更','Custom Post Tag Mutations'=>'自定义文章标签变更','Post Tag Mutations'=>'文章标签变更','Category Mutations'=>'分类变更','Custom Post Category Mutations'=>'自定义文章分类变更','Post Category Mutations'=>'文章分类变更','Category Meta Mutations'=>'分类元数据变更','Custom Post Category Meta Mutations'=>'自定义文章分类元数据变更','Post Category Meta Mutations'=>'文章分类元数据变更','Tag Meta Mutations'=>'标签元数据变更','Custom Post Tag Meta Mutations'=>'自定义文章标签元数据变更','Post Tag Meta Mutations'=>'文章标签元数据变更','Comment Mutations'=>'评论变更','Comment Meta 