,'Server IP Configuration'=>'服务器 IP 配置','General options for the plugin'=>'插件的常规选项','Store and browse plugin logs'=>'存储和浏览插件日志','Configure retrieving the Client IP depending on the platform/environment'=>'根据平台/环境配置客户端 IP 的获取方式','Grant access to users other than admins to edit the GraphQL schema'=>'授权非管理员用户编辑 GraphQL 架构','Enable the Schema tutorial?'=>'启用架构教程？','Add a tutorial page explaining all elements of the GraphQL schema offered by Gato GraphQL, accessible from the menu navigation on the left<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'添加一个教程页面，介绍 Gato GraphQL 提供的 GraphQL 架构的所有元素，可从左侧菜单导航访问<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Enabling the Schema Tutorial page'=>'启用架构教程页面','Plugin setup: Install Persisted Queries for common admin tasks?'=>'插件设置：为常见管理任务安装持久化查询？','When installing or updating the plugin, enable the creation of Persisted Queries that tackle common admin tasks for WordPress?<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'安装或更新插件时，启用创建用于处理 WordPress 常见管理任务的持久化查询？<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Managing the plugin\'s setup data'=>'管理插件的设置数据','Display admin notice with release notes?'=>'显示包含发布说明的管理员通知？','Immediately after upgrading the plugin, show an admin notice with a link to the latest release notes?<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'升级插件后，立即显示一条包含最新发布说明链接的管理员通知？<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Displaying the plugin\'s new features'=>'正在显示插件的新功能','Organize these settings under tabs?'=>'在标签页下组织这些设置？','Have all options in this Settings page be organized under tabs, one tab per module.<br/>After ticking the checkbox, must click on "Save Changes" to be applied<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'将此设置页面中的所有选项按标签页组织，每个模块一个标签页。<br/>勾选复选框后，必须点击“保存更改”才能生效<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Printing the Settings page with tabs or long format'=>'以选项卡或长格式打印设置页面','Enable logs?'=>'启用日志？','Enable storing GraphQL execution logs, accessible via the <strong>%s</strong> menu. %s'=>'启用存储 GraphQL 执行日志，可通过 <strong>%s</strong> 菜单访问。%s','<br/>Log files are stored under folder <code>%s</code>.<br/></br><strong>Important:</strong> Log files can be very large, so it\'s recommended to clear them after a while.'=>'<br/>日志文件存储在文件夹 <code>%s</code> 下。<br/></br><strong>重要：</strong>日志文件可能非常大，建议定期清除。','Enable logs by severity'=>'按严重级别启用日志','Reverse log order?'=>'反转日志顺序？','Display newer log entries first when viewing a log file'=>'查看日志文件时优先显示较新的日志条目','Enable log notifications?'=>'启用日志通知？','Show a badge with the number of log entries in the <strong>%s</strong> menu'=>'在 <strong>%s</strong> 菜单中显示带有日志条目数量的徽标','Enable log notifications by severity'=>'按严重程度启用日志通知','Indicate which severities are included in the badge\'s count'=>'指定哪些严重程度计入徽标的计数','$_SERVER property name to retrieve the client IP'=>'用于获取客户端 IP 的 $_SERVER 属性名称','The visitor\'s IP address is retrieved from under the <code>$_SERVER</code> global variable, by default under property <code>\'REMOTE_ADDR\'</code>; depending on the platform or hosting provider, a different property may need to be used.'=>'访客的 IP 地址从 <code>$_SERVER</code> 全局变量中获取，默认使用属性 <code>\'REMOTE_ADDR\'</code>；根据平台或托管服务提供商的不同，可能需要使用不同的属性。','For instance:'=>'例如：','Cloudflare might use <code>\'HTTP_CF_CONNECTING_IP\'</code>'=>'Cloudflare 可能使用 <code>\'HTTP_CF_CONNECTING_IP\'</code>','AWS might use <code>\'HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR\'</code>'=>'AWS 可能使用 <code>\'HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR\'</code>','others'=>'其他','Which users can edit the schema?'=>'哪些用户可以编辑 schema？','Indicate which users can edit the schema (i.e. creating and updating Persisted Queries, Custom Endpoints, and others)<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'指定哪些用户可以编辑 schema（即创建和更新持久化查询、自定义端点等）<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Managing who can edit the schema'=>'管理谁可以编辑 schema','Critical issues that prevent the operation from completing'=>'阻止操作完成的严重问题','Non-critical issues that may affect the operation'=>'可能影响操作的非严重问题','General information about the operation'=>'关于操作的一般信息','Detailed information for debugging purposes'=>'用于调试目的的详细信息','Indicate which severities are enabled for logging. %s'=>'指定启用哪些严重程度进行日志记录。%s','<br/>Available severities:<br/><ul>%s</ul>'=>'<br/>可用严重程度：<br/><ul>%s</ul>','Error'=>'错误','Warning'=>'警告','Info'=>'信息','Debug'=>'调试','Activate Extensions'=>'激活扩展','Reset Settings'=>'重置设置','Activate Bundles and Extensions from the %s'=>'从 %s 激活套件和扩展','Restore the Gato GraphQL Settings to default values'=>'将 Gato GraphQL 设置恢复为默认值','Adding a license key will <strong>activate the product</strong>'=>'添加许可证密钥将<strong>激活产品</strong>','Removing an existing license key will <strong>deactivate the product</strong>'=>'删除现有许可证密钥将<strong>停用产品</strong>','Updating a license key will first <strong>deactivate the product</strong> (using the previous license key) and then <strong>activate the product</strong> again (using the new license key)'=>'更新许可证密钥将首先<strong>停用产品</strong>（使用旧许可证密钥），然后再次<strong>激活产品</strong>（使用新许可证密钥）','Not updating a license key will <strong>validate the status of the product</strong>'=>'不更新许可证密钥将<strong>验证产品状态</strong>','Enter the license keys for the products purchased on the %s, and click on <strong>Activate licenses (or Deactivate/Validate)</strong>:'=>'输入在 %s 购买的产品的许可证密钥，然后点击<strong>激活许可证（或停用/验证）</strong>：','When clicking on <strong>Activate licenses (or Deactivate/Validate)</strong>, one of the following actions will take place:'=>'点击<strong>激活许可证（或停用/验证）</strong>时，将执行以下操作之一：','(Show details: When are products activated, deactivated or validated?)'=>'（显示详情：产品何时被激活、停用或验证？）','Activate licenses (or Deactivate/Validate)'=>'激活许可证（或停用/验证）','<em>There are no Bundles or Extensions from the %s installed</em>'=>'<em>未安装来自 %s 的套件或扩展</em>','Show options to reset the Settings'=>'显示重置设置的选项','Reset the Gato GraphQL Settings?'=>'重置 Gato GraphQL 设置？','Restore all settings (under tabs <code>%s</code>, <code>%s</code>, <code>%s</code>, <code>%s</code> and <code>%s</code>) to their default values.'=>'将所有设置（位于 <code>%s</code>、<code>%s</code>、<code>%s</code>、<code>%s</code> 和 <code>%s</code> 选项卡下）恢复为默认值。','When the settings are reset, the default values can follow a restrictive or non-restrictive behavior:'=>'重置设置时，默认值可以遵循限制性或非限制性行为：','Feature'=>'功能','Non-restrictive behavior'=>'非限制性行为','Restrictive behavior'=>'限制性行为','“Sensitive” data fields'=>'“敏感”数据字段','Added to the schema'=>'已添加到 Schema','Not added to the schema'=>'未添加到 Schema','Settings from <code>wp_options</code>'=>'来自 <code>wp_options</code> 的设置','All options are queryable'=>'所有选项均可查询','Only a few predefined options are queryable'=>'仅少数预定义选项可查询','Meta (posts, users, comments, taxonomies)'=>'元数据（文章、用户、评论、分类法）','All keys are queryable'=>'所有键均可查询','No keys are queryable'=>'没有键可查询','Max limit to query entities (posts, users, etc)'=>'查询实体（文章、用户等）的最大限制','Unlimited'=>'无限制','Limited'=>'有限制','Environment variables (extension)'=>'环境变量（扩展）','All environment variables and PHP constants are queryable'=>'所有环境变量和 PHP 常量均可查询','No environment variables or PHP constants are queryable'=>'没有环境变量或 PHP 常量可查询','HTTP Client requests (extension)'=>'HTTP 客户端请求（扩展）','All URLs can be requested'=>'所有 URL 均可请求','No URL can be requested'=>'无法请求任何 URL','Choose if to use restrictive or non-restrictive default settings.'=>'选择是否使用限制性或非限制性默认设置。','Use the restrictive default behavior for the Settings'=>'为设置使用限制性默认行为','Use the non-restrictive default behavior for the Settings'=>'为设置使用非限制性默认行为','Confirm: Reset Settings'=>'确认：重置设置','Gato Shop'=>'Gato 商店','Activate Extension Licenses'=>'激活扩展许可证','Schema Namespacing'=>'Schema 命名空间','Response Headers'=>'响应标头','Global Fields'=>'全局字段','Composable Directives'=>'可组合指令','Multi-Field Directives'=>'多字段指令','Mutations'=>'变更','Nested Mutations'=>'嵌套变更','Expose Sensitive Data in the Schema'=>'在 Schema 中公开敏感数据','Self Fields'=>'Self 字段','Global ID Field'=>'全局 ID 字段','Customize the schema accessible to different endpoints, by applying a custom configuration (involving namespacing, access control, cache control, and others) to the grand schema'=>'通过将自定义配置（涉及命名空间、访问控制、缓存控制等）应用于总 Schema，自定义不同端点可访问的 Schema','Automatically namespace types with a vendor/project name, to avoid naming collisions'=>'使用供应商/项目名称自动为类型添加命名空间，以避免命名冲突','Provide custom headers to add to the API response'=>'提供自定义标头以添加到 API 响应中','Fields added to all types in the schema, generally for executing functionality (not retrieving data)'=>'添加到模式中所有类型的字段，通常用于执行功能（而非检索数据）','Have directives modify the behavior of other directives'=>'使指令能够修改其他指令的行为','A single directive can be applied to multiple fields, for performance and extended use cases'=>'单个指令可应用于多个字段，以提升性能并支持扩展用例','Modify data by executing mutations'=>'通过执行 mutation 修改数据','Execute mutations from any type in the schema, not only from the root'=>'从模式中的任意类型执行 mutation，而不仅限于根类型','Expose “sensitive” data elements in the schema'=>'在模式中公开“敏感”数据元素','Expose "self" fields in the schema'=>'在模式中公开 "self" 字段','Uniquely identify objects via field <code>globalID</code> on all types of the GraphQL schema'=>'通过 <code>globalID</code> 字段在 GraphQL 模式的所有类型上唯一标识对象','Namespace the schema?'=>'为模式添加命名空间？','Namespace types in the GraphQL schema?<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'为 GraphQL 模式中的类型添加命名空间？<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Namespacing the schema'=>'为架构添加命名空间','Provide custom headers to add to the API response. One header per line, with format: <code>{header name}: {header value}</code>'=>'提供要添加到 API 响应的自定义标头。每行一个标头，格式为：<code>{header name}: {header value}</code>','Adding custom headers to the GraphQL response (CORS)'=>'向 GraphQL 响应添加自定义标头（CORS）','Do not expose'=>'不公开','Expose under the Root type only'=>'仅在根类型下公开','Expose under all types'=>'在所有类型下公开','Schema exposure.'=>'架构公开。','Under what types to expose global fields.<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'在哪些类型下公开全局字段。<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Hiding Global Fields'=>'隐藏全局字段','Enable multi-field directives?'=>'启用多字段指令？','Enable having a single directive be applied to multiple fields.<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'启用将单个指令应用于多个字段。<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Using multi-field directives'=>'使用多字段指令','Enable composable directives?'=>'启用可组合指令？','Enable adding composable directives (also called "meta-directives", such as <code>@underEachArrayItem</code>, <code>@underArrayItem</code> and <code>@underJSONObjectProperty</code>) to the schema.<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'启用向 schema 添加可组合指令（也称为 "元指令"，例如 <code>@underEachArrayItem</code>、<code>@underArrayItem</code> 和 <code>@underJSONObjectProperty</code>）。<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Using composable directives'=>'使用可组合指令','Use payload types for mutations'=>'为 Mutation 使用载荷类型','Use payload types for mutations, and add fields to query those payload objects'=>'为 Mutation 使用载荷类型，并添加字段以查询这些载荷对象','Do not use payload types for mutations (i.e. return the mutated entity)'=>'不为 Mutation 使用载荷类型（即返回被修改的实体）','Use payload types for all mutations in the schema?'=>'对 schema 中的所有 Mutation 使用载荷类型？','Use payload types for mutations in the schema?<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'对 schema 中的 Mutation 使用载荷类型？<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Returning a payload object or the mutated entity for mutations'=>'为变更操作返回有效载荷对象或被变更的实体','<strong>Use payload types for mutations</strong>:<br/><br/>Mutation fields will return a payload object type, on which we can query the status of the mutation (success or failure), and the error messages (if any) or the successfully mutated entity.<br/><br/><strong>Use payload types for mutations, and add fields to query those payload objects</strong>:<br/><br/>In addition, query fields will be added to retrieve once again those payload objects.<br/><br/><strong>Do not use payload types for mutations (i.e. return the mutated entity)</strong>:<br/><br/>Mutation fields will directly return the mutated entity in case of success or <code>null</code> in case of failure, and any error message will be displayed in the JSON response\'s top-level <code>errors</code> entry.</li></ul>'=>'<strong>为变更操作使用有效载荷类型</strong>:<br/><br/>变更字段将返回一个有效载荷对象类型，通过该对象可以查询变更的状态（成功或失败）、错误消息（如有）或成功变更的实体。<br/><br/><strong>为变更操作使用有效载荷类型，并添加字段以查询这些有效载荷对象</strong>:<br/><br/>此外，还将添加查询字段以再次检索这些有效载荷对象。<br/><br/><strong>不为变更操作使用有效载荷类型（即直接返回被变更的实体）</strong>:<br/><br/>变更字段将在成功时直接返回被变更的实体，失败时返回 <code>null</code>，任何错误消息将显示在 JSON 响应的顶级 <code>errors</code> 条目中。</li></ul>','Do not enable nested mutations'=>'不启用嵌套变更','Enable nested mutations, keeping all mutation fields in the root'=>'启用嵌套变更，保留根类型中的所有变更字段','Enable nested mutations, removing the redundant mutation fields from the root'=>'启用嵌套变更，从根类型中移除冗余的变更字段','Mutation Scheme:'=>'变更方案：','Select the mutation scheme to use in the schema.<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'选择在模式中使用的变更方案。<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Using nested mutations'=>'使用嵌套变更','<strong>Redundant fields:</strong><br/><br/>When nested mutations are enabled, a mutation operation in the <code>Root</code> type may find that another mutation will execute the same operation. As such, the <code>Root</code> mutation could be considered redundant, and removed from the schema.<br/><br/>For instance, if mutation field <code>Post.update</code> is available, mutation field <code>Root.updatePost</code> could be removed.'=>'<strong>冗余字段：</strong><br/><br/>当启用嵌套变更时，<code>Root</code> 类型中的某个变更操作可能发现另一个变更将执行相同的操作。因此，该 <code>Root</code> 变更可被视为冗余，并从模式中移除。<br/><br/>例如，如果变更字段 <code>Post.update</code> 可用，则变更字段 <code>Root.updatePost</code> 可以被移除。','Add “sensitive” fields to the schema?'=>'向模式中添加“敏感”字段？','Expose “sensitive” data elements in the GraphQL schema (such as field <code>Root.roles</code>, field arg <code>Root.posts(status:)</code>, and others), which provide access to potentially private user data.<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'在 GraphQL schema 中暴露“敏感”数据元素（例如字段 <code>Root.roles</code>、字段参数 <code>Root.posts(status:)</code> 等），这些元素可能提供对潜在私密用户数据的访问。<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Querying “sensitive” data fields'=>'查询“敏感”数据字段','Expose the self fields to all types in the schema?'=>'是否将 self 字段暴露给模式中的所有类型？','Expose the <code>self</code> field in the GraphQL schema, which returns an instance of the same object (for whichever type it is applied on), which can be used to adapt the shape of the GraphQL response.<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>'=>'在 GraphQL schema 中暴露 <code>self</code> 字段，该字段返回同一对象的实例（适用于任何类型），可用于调整 GraphQL 响应的结构。<br/>%s<br/><span class="more-info">%s</span>','Querying \'self\' fields'=>'查询 \'self\' 字段','Blocks'=>'块','Comments'=>'评论','User Roles'=>'用户角色','User Avatars'=>'用户头像','Media'=>'媒体','Site'=>'站点','Multisite'=>'多站点','Page Builder'=>'页面构建器','Tags'=>'标签','Post Tags'=>'文章标签','Post Categories'=>'文章分类','Menus'=>'菜单','Custom Posts'=>'自定义文章类型','Query %1$s, through type <code>%2$s</code> added to the schema'=>'查询 %1$s，通过添加到架构中的类型 <code>%2$s</code>','posts'=>'文章','Retrieve the (Gutenberg) blocks contained in the custom post'=>'检索自定义文章中包含的（Gutenberg）块','users'=>'用户','user roles'=>'用户角色','user avatars'=>'用户头像','pages'=>'页面','media elements'=>'媒体元素','comments'=>'评论','post tags'=>'文章标签','post categories'=>'文章分类','menus'=>'菜单','Fetch settings from the site'=>'从站点获取设置','Base functionality for all custom posts'=>'所有自定义文章的基础功能','Fetch site information'=>'获取站点信息','Fetch site information in a WordPress multisite network'=>'在 WordPress 多站点网络中获取站点信息','Fetch data from Page Builders installed on the site'=>'从站点上安装的页面构建器获取数据','Base functionality for all tags'=>'所有标签的基础功能','Base functionality for all categories'=>'所有分类的基础功能','Number of results from querying %s when argument <code>%s</code> is not provided. Use <code>%s</code> for unlimited.'=>'未提供参数 <code>%s</code> 时，查询 %s 所返回的结果数量。使用 <code>%s</code> 表示不限数量。','Maximum number of results from querying %s. Use <code>%s</code> for unlimited.'=>'查询 %s 的最大结果数量。使用 <code>%s</code> 表示不限数量。','This list contains all the "%1$shierarchical" taxonomies which are associated to queryable custom posts, i.e. those selected in "Included custom post types" in the Settings for "Custom Posts". Each %2$s taxonomy\'s associated custom post types is shown under <code>(CPT: ...)</code>. If your desired %2$s taxonomy does not appear here, make sure that all of its associated custom post types are in that allowlist.'=>'此列表包含所有与可查询自定义文章类型关联的 "%1$s层级式"分类法，即在"自定义文章"设置中"包含的自定义文章类型"所选的那些。每个 %2$s 分类法的关联自定义文章类型显示在 <code>(CPT: ...)</code> 下方。如果您所需的 %2$s 分类法未出现在此处，请确保其所有关联的自定义文章类型均已加入该允许列表。','custom posts'=>'自定义文章','media items'=>'媒体项目','tags'=>'标签','categories'=>'分类','Default limit for %s'=>'%s 的默认限制','Max limit for %s'=>'%s 的最大限制','Included custom post types'=>'包含的自定义文章类型','Select the custom post types that can be queried, to be accessible via <code>%s</code>. A custom post type will be represented by its own type in the schema if available (such as <code>%s</code> or <code>%s</code>) or, otherwise, via <code>%s</code>.<br/>%s<br/>%s'=>'选择可查询的自定义文章类型，可通过 <code>%s</code> 访问。自定义文章类型在架构中将以其自身类型表示（如有，例如 <code>%s</code> 或 <code>%s</code>），否则通过 <code>%s</code> 表示。<br/>%s<br/>%s','Use single type instead of union type?'=>'使用单一类型而非联合类型？','If type <code>%s</code> is composed of only one type (eg: <code>%s</code>), then directly return this single type, instead of the union type?'=>'如果类型 <code>%s</code> 仅由一种类型组成（例如：<code>%s</code>），是否直接返回该单一类型，而非联合类型？','custom post status'=>'自定义文章状态','custom post raw content fields (<code>rawContent</code>, <code>rawTitle</code> and <code>rawExcerpt</code>)'=>'自定义文章原始内容字段（<code>rawContent</code>、<code>rawTitle</code> 和 <code>rawExcerpt</code>）','custom post edit link'=>'自定义文章编辑链接','user email'=>'用户邮箱','%s (CPT: "%s")'=>'%s（CPT："%s"）','Included tag taxonomies'=>'包含的标签分类法','non-'=>'非','tag'=>'标签','Select the tag taxonomies that can be queried, to be accessible via <code>%s</code>. A tag taxonomy will be represented by its own type in the schema if available (such as <code>%s</code>) or, otherwise, via <code>%s</code>.<br/>%s<br/>%s'=>'选择可查询的标签分类法，可通过 <code>%s</code> 访问。标签分类法在架构中将以其自身类型表示（如有，例如 <code>%s</code>），否则通过 <code>%s</code> 表示。<br/>%s<br/>%s','Included category taxonomies'=>'包含的分类分类法','category'=>'分类','Select the category taxonomies that can be queried, to be accessible via <code>%s</code>. A tag taxonomy will be represented by its own type in the schema if available (such as <code>%s</code>) or, otherwise, via <code>%s</code>.<br/>%s<br/>%s'=>'选择可查询的分类分类法，可通过 <code>%s</code> 访问。标签分类法在架构中将以其自身类型表示（如有，例如 <code>%s</code>），否则通过 <code>%s</code> 表示。<br/>%s<br/>%s','menu item raw title'=>'菜单项原始标题','If type <code>%s</code> is composed of only one type (<code>%s</code>), then directly return this single type, instead of the union type?'=>'如果类型 <code>%s</code> 仅由一种类型组成（<code>%s</code>），是否直接返回该单一类型，而非联合类型？','block type registry'=>'区块类型注册表','Default limit for querying comments in the Root'=>'在根查询评论的默认限制','Default limit for querying comments under a custom post or comment'=>'在自定义文章或评论下查询评论的默认限制','%s and %s'=>'%s 和 %s','Max limit for querying comments'=>'查询评论的最大限制','comment status'=>'评论状态','comment raw content'=>'评论原始内容','Settings entries'=>'设置条目','<strong>Example:</strong> Any of these entries match option name <code>"%1$s"</code>: %2$s'=>'<strong>示例：</strong>以下任何条目均匹配选项名称 <code>"%1$s"</code>：%2$s','List of all the option names, to either allow or deny access to, when querying fields <code>%s</code>, <code>%s</code>, <code>%s</code> and <code>%s</code> (one entry per line).'=>'查询字段 <code>%s</code>、<code>%s</code>、<code>%s</code> 和 <code>%s</code> 时，用于允许或拒绝访问的所有选项名称列表（每行一个条目）。','Default avatar size'=>'默认头像尺寸','Size of the avatar (in pixels) when not providing argument <code>"size"</code> in field <code>%s.avatar</code>'=>'在字段 <code>%s.avatar</code> 中未提供参数 <code>"size"</code> 时的头像尺寸（像素）','user capabilities'=>'用户权限','Excerpt as Description'=>'将摘要作为描述','Welcome Guides'=>'欢迎指南','Additional Gato GraphQL Documentation'=>'Gato GraphQL 附加文档','Provide a description of the different entities (Custom Endpoints, Persisted Queries, and others) through their excerpt'=>'通过摘要为不同实体（自定义端点、持久化查询及其他）提供描述','Display welcome guides which demonstrate how to use the plugin\'s different functionalities. <em>It requires WordPress version \'%s\' or above, or Gutenberg version \'%s\' or above</em>'=>'显示欢迎指南，演示如何使用插件的不同功能。<em>需要 WordPress 版本 \'%s\' 或更高版本，或 Gutenberg 版本 \'%s\' 或更高版本</em>','Documentation on using the Gato GraphQL'=>'Gato GraphQL 使用文档','Please rate Gato GraphQL ❤️'=>'请为 Gato GraphQL 评分 ❤️','We work really hard to deliver a plugin that converts the WordPress site into a full-fledged GraphQL server. It takes plenty of time and effort to develop, test and maintain the free Gato GraphQL plugin. Therefore if you like what you see and appreciate our work, we ask you nothing more than to please rate the plugin in the directory. Thanks in advance!'=>'我们付出了大量努力，打造一款将 WordPress 网站转化为完整 GraphQL 服务器的插件。开发、测试和维护免费的 Gato GraphQL 插件需要耗费大量时间和精力。因此，如果您喜欢我们的工作并认可我们的付出，我们只请求您在目录中为该插件评分。提前感谢！','Rate Plugin'=>'为插件评分','Plugin <strong>Gato GraphQL</strong> has been updated to version <code>%s</code>. <strong><a href="%s" class="%s">Check out what\'s new</a></strong> | <a href="%s">Disable this admin notice in the Settings</a>'=>'插件 <strong>Gato GraphQL</strong> 已更新至版本 <code>%s</code>。<strong><a href="%s" class="%s">查看新功能</a></strong> | <a href="%s">在设置中禁用此管理员通知</a>','Go PRO'=>'升级专业版','Nested mutations'=>'嵌套变更','Bulk mutations'=>'批量变更','Admin'=>'管理','Internal admin tasks'=>'内部管理任务','Webhook'=>'Webhook','Process data from external services'=>'处理来自外部服务的数据','The extension with class \'%s\' has not been registered yet'=>'类 \'%s\' 的扩展尚未注册','The license is invalid. Please <a href="%s">enter a new license key in %s</a> to enable it'=>'许可证无效。请<a href="%s">在 %s 中输入新的许可证密钥</a>以启用它','The provided license key belongs to a different extension. Please <a href="%s">enter the right license key in %s</a> to enable it'=>'提供的许可证密钥属于其他扩展。请<a href="%s">在 %s 中输入正确的许可证密钥</a>以启用它','Please <a href="%s">enter the license key in %s</a> to enable it'=>'请<a href="%s">在 %s 中输入许可证密钥</a>以启用它','The license is invalid. Please enter a new license key to enable it'=>'许可证无效。请输入新的许可证密钥以启用它','The provided license key belongs to a different extension. Please enter the right license key to enable it'=>'提供的许可证密钥属于其他扩展。请输入正确的许可证密钥以启用它','Please enter the license key to enable it'=>'请输入许可证密钥以启用它','<strong>%s</strong>: %s.'=>'<strong>%s</strong>: %s.','Gato GraphQL PRO'=>'Gato GraphQL PRO','<p><em>(This message is visible only by the admin.)</em></p>'=>'<p><em>（此消息仅对管理员可见。）</em></p>','<p>Something went wrong initializing plugin <strong>%s</strong> (so it has not been loaded):</p><code>%s</code><p>Stack trace:</p><pre>%s</pre>'=>'<p>初始化插件 <strong>%s</strong> 时出错（因此未加载）：</p><code>%s</code><p>堆栈跟踪：</p><pre>%s</pre>','Module \'%s\' does not exist'=>'模块 \'%s\' 不存在','Module type \'%s\' does not exist'=>'模块类型 \'%s\' 不存在','Settings Category \'%s\' does not exist'=>'设置类别 \'%s\' 不存在','User authorization scheme with name \'%s\' does not exist'=>'名称为 \'%s\' 的用户授权方案不存在','No user authorization scheme has been registered'=>'未注册任何用户授权方案','Users with capability: "%s"'=>'具有权限的用户："%s"','Users with role: "%s"'=>'具有角色的用户："%s"','Users with any role: "%s"'=>'具有任意角色的用户："%s"','Query execution (endpoint/persisted query)'=>'查询执行（端点/持久化查询）','Schema Configuration for GraphQL'=>'GraphQL 的 Schema 配置','You need to run `npm start` or `npm run build` for the "%s" block first.'=>'您需要先为 "%s" 块运行 `npm start` 或 `npm run build`。','Operations'=>'操作','Fields'=>'字段','Directives'=>'指令','Select schema elements'=>'选择 Schema 元素','Configuration:'=>'配置：','Options'=>'选项','Enabled:'=>'已启用：','Customize configuration? (Or use default from Settings?)'=>'自定义配置？（或使用设置中的默认值？）','Use configuration from Settings'=>'使用设置中的配置','Use custom configuration'=>'使用自定义配置','Undefined item with ID %s'=>'ID 为 %s 的项目未定义','(not set)'=>'（未设置）','Default'=>'默认','Inherit from parent'=>'从父级继承','✅ Yes'=>'✅ 是','❌ No'=>'❌ 否','⚫️ Do not expose'=>'⚫️ 不公开','🔵 Expose under the Root type only'=>'🔵 仅在 Root 类型下公开','⚪️ Expose under all types'=>'⚪️ 在所有类型下公开','Schema exp