thub.io/graphql-spec/draft/#sel-HAJbLAuDABCBIu9N）','The type of the nested type (available for NonNull and List types only) as defined by the GraphQL spec (https://graphql.github.io/graphql-spec/draft/#sel-HAJbLA4DABCBIu9N)'=>'嵌套类型的类型（仅适用于 NonNull 和 List 类型），如 GraphQL 规范所定义（https://graphql.github.io/graphql-spec/draft/#sel-HAJbLA4DABCBIu9N）','A scalar specification URL (a String (in the form of a URL) for custom scalars, otherwise must be null) as defined by the GraphQL spec (https://spec.graphql.org/draft/#sel-IAJXNFA0EABABL9N)'=>'标量规范 URL（自定义标量为字符串形式的 URL，否则必须为 null），由 GraphQL 规范定义（https://spec.graphql.org/draft/#sel-IAJXNFA0EABABL9N）','`true` for OneOf Input Objects, `false` otherwise'=>'`true` 用于 OneOf 输入对象，`false` 用于其他情况','Extensions (custom metadata) added to the GraphQL type (for all \'named\' types: Object, Interface, Union, Scalar, Enum and InputObject) (see: https://github.com/graphql/graphql-spec/issues/300#issuecomment-504734306 and below comments, and https://github.com/graphql/graphql-js/issues/1527)'=>'添加到 GraphQL 类型的扩展项（自定义元数据）（适用于所有 \'named\' 类型：Object、Interface、Union、Scalar、Enum 和 InputObject）（参见：https://github.com/graphql/graphql-spec/issues/300#issuecomment-504734306 及下方评论，以及 https://github.com/graphql/graphql-js/issues/1527）','edit schema:'=>'编辑架构：','enable nested mutations:'=>'启用嵌套变更：','enable GraphQL introspection:'=>'启用 GraphQL 内省：','Unknown type kind \'%s\''=>'未知的类型种类\'%s\'','Cannot recognize GraphQL Operation AST object, with class \'%s\''=>'无法识别 GraphQL 操作 AST 对象，类名为 \'%s\'','("Schema" type directive)'=>'("Schema" 类型指令)',' _%s_'=>' _%s_','(Version: %s)'=>'(版本：%s)','[Mutation] %s'=>'[Mutation] %s','A Schema Definition Reference Object with id \'%s\\s has already been registered'=>'ID 为 \'%s\\s 的 Schema 定义引用对象已被注册','The Schema object data must be unique, so must not create object with ID "%s"'=>'Schema 对象数据必须唯一，因此不得创建 ID 为 "%s" 的对象','Extensions (custom metadata) added to the directive'=>'添加到指令的扩展（自定义元数据）','A GraphQL directive in the data graph'=>'数据图中的 GraphQL 指令','Extensions (custom metadata) added to the enum value'=>'添加到枚举值的扩展（自定义元数据）','Representation of an Enum value in GraphQL'=>'GraphQL 中枚举值的表示','Extensions (custom metadata) added to the field'=>'添加到字段的扩展（自定义元数据）','Representation of a GraphQL type\'s field'=>'GraphQL 类型字段的表示','Extensions (custom metadata) added to the input value'=>'添加到输入值的扩展（自定义元数据）','Representation of an input object in GraphQL'=>'GraphQL 中输入对象的表示','Mutation type, starting from which mutations are executed'=>'变更类型，从此处开始执行变更操作','Extensions (custom metadata) added to the GraphQL type (for all \'named\' types: Object, Interface, Union, Scalar, Enum and InputObject)'=>'添加到 GraphQL 类型的扩展项（自定义元数据）（适用于所有 \'named\' 类型：Object、Interface、Union、Scalar、Enum 和 InputObject）','Query type, starting from which the query is executed'=>'查询类型，从该类型开始执行查询','Schema type, to implement the introspection fields'=>'Schema 类型，用于实现自省字段','Representation of each GraphQL type in the graph'=>'图中每种 GraphQL 类型的表示','The name of the dynamic variable under which to export the array element value from the current iteration'=>'从当前迭代中导出数组元素值所使用的动态变量名称','The name of the dynamic variable under which to export the array element key from the current iteration'=>'从当前迭代中导出数组元素键所使用的动态变量名称','Directive \'%s\' from field \'%s\' cannot be applied on object with ID \'%s\' because it is not of a supported type'=>'指令 \'%s\' 来自字段 \'%s\'，无法应用于 ID 为 \'%s\' 的对象，因为它不属于受支持的类型','Directive \'%s\' from field \'%s\' cannot be applied on object with ID \'%s\' because it is not a string'=>'指令 \'%s\' 来自字段 \'%s\'，无法应用于 ID 为 \'%s\' 的对象，因为它不是字符串','Directive \'%s\' from field \'%s\' cannot be applied on object with ID \'%s\' because it is not a bool'=>'指令 \'%s\' 来自字段 \'%s\'，无法应用于 ID 为 \'%s\' 的对象，因为它不是布尔值','Directive \'%s\' from field \'%s\' cannot be applied on object with ID \'%s\' because it is not an integer'=>'指令 \'%s\' 来自字段 \'%s\'，无法应用于 ID 为 \'%s\' 的对象，因为它不是整数','Directive \'%s\' from field \'%s\' cannot be applied on object with ID \'%s\' because it is not a float'=>'指令 \'%s\' 来自字段 \'%s\'，无法应用于 ID 为 \'%s\' 的对象，因为它不是浮点数','Directive \'%s\' from field \'%s\' cannot be applied on object with ID \'%s\' because it is not a JSON object'=>'指令 \'%s\' 来自字段 \'%s\'，无法应用于 ID 为 \'%s\' 的对象，因为它不是 JSON 对象','Directive \'%s\' from field \'%s\' cannot be applied on object with ID \'%s\' because it is not an array'=>'指令 \'%s\' 来自字段 \'%s\'，无法应用于 ID 为 \'%s\' 的对象，因为它不是数组','Dynamic variable with name \'%s\' had already been set, had its value overridden'=>'名为 \'%s\' 的动态变量已被设置，其值已被覆盖','Dynamic variable with name \'%s\' had already been set for object with ID \'%s\', had its value overridden'=>'名称为\'%s\'的动态变量已为ID为\'%s\'的对象设置，其值已被覆盖','The format for type \'%s\' is not correct: it must be satisfied via regex /(\\+{1}[0-9]{1,3}[0-9]{8,9})/'=>'类型\'%s\'的格式不正确：必须满足正则表达式/(\\+{1}[0-9]{1,3}[0-9]{8,9})/','The format for type \'%s\' is not correct: it must be satisfied via regex /^{?[A-Z0-9]{8}-[A-Z0-9]{4}-[A-Z0-9]{4}-[A-Z0-9]{4}-[A-Z0-9]{12}}?$/'=>'类型\'%s\'的格式不正确：必须满足正则表达式/^{?[A-Z0-9]{8}-[A-Z0-9]{4}-[A-Z0-9]{4}-[A-Z0-9]{4}-[A-Z0-9]{12}}?$/','Type \'%s\' must receive arrays as values (even for single-item values, eg: `{ some_key: [ "some value" ] }`), but received: `%s`'=>'类型\'%s\'必须接收数组作为值（即使是单项值，例如：`{ some_key: [ "some value" ] }`），但收到的是：`%s`','The format for type \'%s\' is not correct: it must be satisfied via regex /^[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$/'=>'类型\'%s\'的格式不正确：必须满足正则表达式/^[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*$/','Index \'%s\' is not set for array: %s'=>'数组中未设置索引\'%s\'：%s','Key or path \'%s\' is not reachable for object: %s'=>'对象中键或路径\'%s\'不可访问：%s','The item under index \'%s\' (with value \'%s\') is not an array'=>'索引\'%s\'下的项目（值为\'%s\'）不是数组','The item under path \'%s\' (with value \'%s\') is not an array'=>'路径\'%s\'下的项目（值为\'%s\'）不是数组','Oneof input to navigate to some JSON object property, whether on the object\'s first level (via `key`) or deeper (via `path`)'=>'Oneof输入，用于导航到某个JSON对象属性，无论是对象的第一层（通过`key`）还是更深层（通过`path`）','Query a property from the object\'s first level'=>'从对象的第一层查询属性','Query a property on a deeper level of the object, using `.` to navigate the levels (eg: use "contact.email" to retrieve the value from `{ contact: { email: "hi@there.com" } }`)'=>'使用`.`导航层级，查询对象更深层的属性（例如：使用"contact.email"从`{ contact: { email: "hi@there.com" } }`中检索值）','Custom scalar representing a JSON Object where values are lists (of anything)%s'=>'自定义标量，表示值为列表（任意类型）的JSON对象%s',' or null'=>' 或null','"Always `null`" scalar, to indicate the the field will always be resolved as `null`'=>'"始终为`null`"标量，表示该字段将始终解析为`null`','Custom scalar representing a JSON Object with exactly 2 properties: code (of type Int or String) and name (of type String)'=>'自定义标量，表示具有恰好2个属性的JSON对象：code（Int或String类型）和name（String类型）','Domain scalar, such as https://mysite.com or http://www.mysite.org'=>'域名标量，例如https://mysite.com或http://www.mysite.org','An identifier string scalar type that validates the string matches the pattern [a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*.'=>'一种标识符字符串标量类型，验证字符串是否匹配模式[a-zA-Z_][a-zA-Z0-9_]*。','Custom scalar representing a JSON Object where values are IDs (strings or integers)'=>'自定义标量，表示值为ID（字符串或整数）的JSON对象','Custom scalar representing a JSON Object where values are integers'=>'自定义标量，表示值为整数的JSON对象','IP scalar, including both IPv4 (such as 192.168.0.1) and IPv6 (such as 2001:0db8:85a3:08d3:1319:8a2e:0370:7334)'=>'IP标量，包括IPv4（如192.168.0.1）和IPv6（如2001:0db8:85a3:08d3:1319:8a2e:0370:7334）','IPv4 scalar, such as 192.168.0.1'=>'IPv4标量，例如192.168.0.1','IPv6 scalar, such as 2001:0db8:85a3:08d3:1319:8a2e:0370:7334'=>'IPv6标量，例如2001:0db8:85a3:08d3:1319:8a2e:0370:7334','MAC (media access control) address scalar, such as 00:1A:C2:7B:00:47'=>'MAC（媒体访问控制）地址标量，例如00:1A:C2:7B:00:47','A non-empty string scalar type that validates the string is not empty.'=>'一种非空字符串标量类型，验证字符串是否不为空。','Phone number scalar, such as +1-212-555-0149'=>'电话号码标量，例如+1-212-555-0149','A positive float or 0.'=>'正浮点数或0。','A positive integer or 0.'=>'正整数或0。','A positive float (> 0).'=>'正浮点数（> 0）。','A positive 