rts with "/", followed by the URL relative path'=>'URL 绝对路径标量，例如 URL "https://mysite.com/my-fabulous-page" 中的 "/my-fabulous-page"。绝对路径以 "/" 开头，后跟 URL 相对路径','URL scalar, such as https://mysite.com/my-fabulous-page'=>'URL 标量，例如 https://mysite.com/my-fabulous-page','Custom scalar representing an XML string'=>'表示 XML 字符串的自定义标量','Cannot provide blocks to exclude and include at the same time'=>'不能同时提供要排除和要包含的块','Error parsing post ID %d: This post does not appear to contain block content.'=>'解析文章 ID %d 时出错：该文章似乎不包含块内容。','This fields is designed to parse Gutenberg blocks and can not read classic editor content.'=>'此字段用于解析 Gutenberg 块，无法读取经典编辑器内容。','This post either does not contain block content, or its block content has errors. (Edit the post within the WordPress editor, fix the errors, save, and try again.)'=>'该文章不包含块内容，或其块内容存在错误。（请在 WordPress 编辑器中编辑该文章，修复错误后保存，然后重试。）','Block name'=>'块名称','Block attributes, parsed to the type declared in their block.json schema'=>'块属性，解析为其 block.json 架构中声明的类型','Block\'s inner blocks (if suitable)'=>'块的内部块（如适用）','Block\'s whole HTML code, including the block comment delimiters'=>'块的完整 HTML 代码，包括块注释分隔符','Attribute name'=>'属性名称','Name of the block type owning this attribute'=>'拥有此属性的块类型名称','JSON-Schema "type" of the attribute (e.g. "string", "boolean"). Returns the first type if it\'s a union.'=>'属性的 JSON-Schema "type"（例如 "string"、"boolean"）。如果是联合类型，则返回第一个类型。','Human-readable label for the attribute (used by auto-generated controls in WP 7.0+)'=>'属性的人类可读标签（由 WP 7.0+ 中的自动生成控件使用）','Default value of the attribute'=>'属性的默认值','Allowed values, if the attribute is restricted to an enum'=>'允许的值（如果属性限定为枚举）','Where the attribute value is parsed from (e.g. "attribute", "html", "text"); null when stored in block-comment delimiters'=>'属性值的解析来源（例如 "attribute"、"html"、"text"）；当存储于块注释分隔符中时为 null','Attribute role (e.g. "local", "content")'=>'属性角色（例如 "local"、"content"）','Whether WordPress auto-generates an editor control for this attribute (PHP-only blocks, WP 7.0+)'=>'WordPress 是否为该属性自动生成编辑器控件（仅限 PHP 块，WP 7.0+）','Full attribute schema as a JSON object'=>'完整的属性架构（以 JSON 对象表示）','Block name (e.g. "core/paragraph")'=>'区块名称（例如 "core/paragraph"）','Block "supports" configuration as registered in `block.json`, returned as a JSON object'=>'在 `block.json` 中注册的区块 "supports" 配置，以 JSON 对象返回','Whether this block has a registered `render_callback` (i.e. is a dynamic/PHP-rendered block)'=>'此区块是否已注册 `render_callback`（即是否为动态/PHP 渲染区块）','The block\'s registered attributes'=>'区块已注册的属性','The names of the block\'s registered attributes'=>'区块已注册属性的名称','(Gutenberg) Blocks in a custom post'=>'（Gutenberg）自定义文章中的区块','(Gutenberg) Block data items (as JSON objects) in a custom post'=>'（Gutenberg）自定义文章中的区块数据项（以 JSON 对象表示）','(Gutenberg) Flattened array containing the block data items (as JSON objects) in a custom post, and replacing property \'innerBlocks\' with \'innerBlockPositions\', indicating the position of the inner blocks in the array (starting from 0)'=>'（Gutenberg）包含自定义文章中区块数据项（以 JSON 对象表示）的扁平化数组，并将属性 \'innerBlocks\' 替换为 \'innerBlockPositions\'，指示内部区块在数组中的位置（从 0 开始）','Indicate if to use the HTML5 parser when converting block content. When parsing HTML5, the parser will convert non-regular breaking spaces, such as "U+00A0", to "&nbsp;" entities.'=>'指示在转换区块内容时是否使用 HTML5 解析器。解析 HTML5 时，解析器会将非常规换行空格（如 "U+00A0"）转换为 "&nbsp;" 实体。','All registered block types in the WordPress block registry'=>'WordPress 区块注册表中所有已注册的区块类型','Input to filter the attributes of a block type'=>'用于筛选区块类型属性的输入','Filter attributes by their JSON-Schema "type" property. An attribute matches if any of its declared types is in the provided list.'=>'按 JSON-Schema "type" 属性筛选属性。如果某个属性声明的任意类型在所提供的列表中，则视为匹配。','Filter attributes that have (or do not have) an auto-generated editor control. Available since WordPress 7.0.'=>'筛选具有（或不具有）自动生成的编辑器控件的属性。自 WordPress 7.0 起可用。','Filter attributes that are (or are not) restricted to a list of allowed values via the `enum` schema property'=>'筛选通过 `enum` 架构属性限制（或未限制）为允许值列表的属性','Filter block types by their `supports` configuration'=>'按 `supports` 配置筛选区块类型','Filter blocks registered fully in PHP (PHP-only blocks). Available since WordPress 7.0.'=>'筛选完全在 PHP 中注册的区块（纯 PHP 区块）。自 WordPress 7.0 起可用。','Filter blocks supporting the `anchor` attribute'=>'筛选支持 `anchor` 属性的区块','Filter blocks supporting alignment'=>'筛选支持对齐的区块','Filter blocks supporting the auto-generated className'=>'筛选支持自动生成 className 的区块','Filter blocks supporting a custom className'=>'筛选支持自定义 className 的区块','Filter blocks supporting direct HTML editing'=>'筛选支持直接编辑 HTML 的区块','Filter blocks shown in the inserter'=>'筛选显示在插入器中的区块','Filter blocks that may be inserted multiple times in a post'=>'筛选可在文章中多次插入的区块','Filter blocks that can be converted into reusable blocks'=>'筛选可转换为可复用区块的区块','Input to configure which properties to include in the block data'=>'用于配置区块数据中包含哪些属性的输入','Include the innerContent property in the block data'=>'在区块数据中包含 innerContent 属性','Input to filter the registered block types'=>'用于筛选已注册区块类型的输入','Limit results to block types with these names (e.g. "core/paragraph")'=>'将结果限制为具有这些名称的区块类型（例如 "core/paragraph"）','Exclude block types with these names'=>'排除具有这些名称的区块类型','Filter block types whose name contains the given substring'=>'筛选名称包含指定子字符串的区块类型','Filter by `supports` configuration. e.g. `{ autoRegister: true }` returns PHP-only blocks (WP 7.0+)'=>'按 `supports` 配置筛选。例如，`{ autoRegister: true }` 返回纯 PHP 区块（WP 7.0+）','Filter blocks that do (or do not) have a registered `render_callback`'=>'筛选已注册（或未注册）`render_callback` 的区块','Entities representing a Block'=>'表示区块的实体','Block'=>'区块','A registered attribute of a block type, as defined in its block.json schema'=>'区块类型的已注册属性，如其 block.json 架构中所定义','A block type registered in the WordPress block registry'=>'在 WordPress 区块注册表中注册的区块类型','Representation of a Block that works for all blocks, retrieving the block attributes as a non-strictly-typed JSON object'=>'适用于所有区块的区块表示，以非严格类型的 JSON 对象形式获取区块属性','JSON-Schema "type" of a block attribute. Includes `null`, so it can\'t be a GraphQL Enum (which disallows that name).'=>'区块属性的 JSON-Schema "type"。包含 `null`，因此不能作为 GraphQL Enum（该名称不被允许）。','Union of \'Block\' types'=>'\'Block\' 类型的联合','Comment karma'=>'评论积分','The author IP'=>'作者IP地址','Order by author email'=>'按作者邮箱排序','Order by author IP'=>'按作者IP排序','Order by author URL'=>'按作者URL排序','Order by karma'=>'按积分排序','Skip ordering'=>'跳过排序','Custom post raw status (as it exists in the database, eg: `publish` instead of `future`)'=>'自定义文章的原始状态（数据库中的实际值，例如：`publish` 而非 `future`）','The URL in the wp-admin to edit the custom post, or `null` if the user has no permissions to access it'=>'在wp-admin中编辑该自定义文章的URL，若用户无访问权限则返回 `null`','Menu order'=>'菜单顺序','Get the custom post ID from a URL'=>'从URL获取自定义文章ID','The URL to convert to a custom post ID'=>'要转换为自定义文章ID的URL','The menu order'=>'菜单顺序','Order by number of comments'=>'按评论数排序','Order by a random number'=>'按随机数排序','Order by last modified date'=>'按最后修改日期排序','Order by relevance'=>'按相关性排序','Order by custom post parent id'=>'按自定义文章父级ID排序','Order by menu order'=>'按菜单顺序排序','Future content'=>'未来内容','Private content'=>'私有内容','Inherit content'=>'继承内容','Indicate if to include custom posts which are password-protected. Pass `null` to fetch both with/out password'=>'指定是否包含受密码保护的自定义文章。传入 `null` 以同时获取有/无密码的文章','Include custom posts protected by a specific password'=>'包含受特定密码保护的自定义文章','Future content - custom posts to publish in the future'=>'未来内容 - 计划在未来发布的自定义文章','Private content - not visible to users who are not logged in'=>'私有内容 - 未登录用户不可见','Used with a child custom post (such as Attachments and Revisions) to determine the actual status from the parent custom post'=>'与子级自定义文章（如附件和修订版本）配合使用，从父级自定义文章确定实际状态','Any custom post status'=>'任意自定义文章状态','Custom post the media item is attached to.'=>'媒体项目所附加的自定义文章。','Media element URL'=>'媒体元素URL','Media element URL path'=>'媒体元素URL路径','Media element slug'=>'媒体元素别名','Gets the available intermediate image size names.'=>'获取可用的中间图片尺寸名称。','Query media item by slug'=>'按别名查询媒体项目','Menu\'s name'=>'菜单名称','Menu\'s slug'=>'菜单别名','Number of items contained in the menu'=>'菜单中包含的项目数量','To which locations has the menu been assigned to'=>'该菜单已分配到的位置','Query by slug'=>'按别名查询','Query by location'=>'按位置查询','Filter menus based on locations'=>'根据位置筛选菜单','Menu Locations'=>'菜单位置','Filter elements by meta key and value'=>'按元键和值筛选元素','Order by meta value. See description for ‘meta_value‘ in: https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/classes/wp_query/#order-orderby-parameters'=>'按元值排序。请参阅以下链接中 \'meta_value\' 的说明：https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/classes/wp_query/#order-orderby-parameters','Operators to compare against an array value'=>'与数组值比较的运算符','Operators to compare against the meta key'=>'与元键比较的运算符','Operators to compare against a numeric value'=>'与数值比较的运算符','Operators to compare against a string value'=>'与字符串值比较的运算符','Custom field type'=>'自定义字段类型','Filter by meta key and value. The key must be allowed access in the Settings. See: https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/classes/wp_meta_query/'=>'按元键和值筛选。该键必须在设置中被允许访问。请参阅：https://developer.wordpress.org/reference/classes/wp_meta_query/','Custom field key'=>'自定义字段键','Value and operator to compare against'=>'用于比较的值和运算符','OR or AND, how the sub-arrays should be compared. Default: AND. Only the value from the first sub-array will be used'=>'OR 或 AND，子数组的比较方式。默认值：AND。仅使用第一个子数组中的值','Custom field value'=>'自定义字段值','The operator to compare against'=>'用于比较的运算符','Compare against the meta key'=>'与元键进行比较','Compare against a numeric meta value'=>'与数值类型的元值进行比较','Compare against a string meta value'=>'与字符串类型的元值进行比较','Compare against an array meta value'=>'与数组类型的元值进行比较','Site\'s ID (within the multisite)'=>'站点 ID（在多站点网络中）','Site\'s name'=>'站点名称','Site\'s URL'=>'站点 URL','Site\'s locale'=>'站点语言区域','Site\'s language'=>'站点语言','Sites in the WordPress multisite network'=>'WordPress 多站点网络中的站点','Number of sites in the WordPress multisite network'=>'WordPress 多站点